    <etym xml:lang="ru">Из %iærm-cæf%i, от <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arm"/> ‘рука’ и <ref
            type="xr" target="#entry_cæf"/> ‘удар’, как <mentioned xml:lang="os-x-iron"
                ><lang/><w>æmʒæǧd</w></mentioned> из %iærm-caǧd%i. Выпадение %im%i закономерно для
        дигорского; ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ar"/> ‘оглобля’ (← „рука“); в сложных словах
        %im%i выпадает в обоих диалектах, ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærxūd"/>.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">From %iærm-cæf%i, derived from <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arm"/> ‘hand’
            and<ref type="xr" target="#entry_cæf"/> ‘punch’, like <mentioned xml:lang="os-x-iron"
                ><lang/><w>æmʒæǧd</w></mentioned> from %iærm-caǧd%i. The loss of %im%i is regural
        for Digor, compare <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ar"/> ‘shaft’ (← ‘hand’); in complex words
        %im%i falls out in both dialects, compare <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærxūd"/>.</etym>
